lf of the projects cost and will be provided over three years subject to annual appropriations estar electric vanedit the estar was an allelectric van production began in march  and first deliveries began two months later via its workhorse group division the technology used in estar was licensed to navistar in  in a joint venture with modec and navistar bought the intellectual property rights from the modecs bankruptcy administrators in  the introduction of the estar was supported by a us million us department of energy stimulus grant under the  american recovery and reinvestment act the estar had a  lb  kg payload capacity available with a  or foot cargo box the vehicle was powered by a  kw  hp electric motor powered by an kwhr lithiumion battery pack supplied by a systems and also used regenerative braking the electric van had a range of  mi  km and a full charge took between  and  hours by may  the estar had received us environmental protection agency epa and carb certifications the estar also met all federal motor vehicle safety standards fmvss the first vans were delivered in may  to fedex express for use in los angeles other customers included pacific gas and electric company pge the cocacola company and canada post the estar had a price of us navistar discontinued the estar van in march  as part of a corporate restructuring plan to focus on current profitability criticismedit in december  the nonpartisan organization public campaign criticized navistar international for spending  million on lobbying and not paying any taxes during  instead getting  million in tax rebates despite making a profit of  million and increasing executive pay by  on jan   navistar financial said it would restate financial statements for fiscal years  and  and the first three quarters of fiscal  because it did not take into consideration potential changes to future income on april   navistar restated financial results from  through  and for the first three quarters of  due to accounting practices that are the subject of a continuing review imagesedit navistar international vehicles  international lonestar tractor truck  idf custom international  ic bus ce school bus  international durastar mediumduty truck  international  scd   wikimedia commons has media related to navistar trucks wikimedia commons has media related to international trucks see alsoedit chicago portal illinois portal companies portal trucks portal international harvester list of international harvester vehicles odyne corporation referencesedit  httpsfinanceyahoocomquotenavfinancialspnav  httpsfinanceyahoocomquotenavprofilepnav  warrenville for navistar  real estate  crains chicago business chicagobusinesscom  retrieved    chicago plant rocked by workplace shooting occupationalhazardscom  retrieved    a b navistar closing down workhorse to cut costs rv business  september  archived from the original on  november     archived june   at the wayback machine  deloitte partner disciplined over navistar auditpermanent dead link cnn october    a b navistar international corp  form k  annual report pdf filesshareholdercom retrieved    navistar forms unit to sell trucks products to military  topnews  drivers  topnews truckinginfocom  retrieved    international truck and engine first company to enter hybrid commercial truck production november   fuerteventura digital  canada navistar defense retrieved    a b c navistar international corporation  investor relations irnavistarcom  retrieved    nav  nyse irnavistarcom  retrieved    subscription center chicagobusinesscom retrieved    navistar international corporation  investor relations irnavistarcom  retrieved    navistar international co  annual report irnavistarcom  retrieved    eloise lee  robert johnson  top  us defense companies business insider retrieved    in  we expect our us military sales to continue to decline contributing to the decline are the budgetary constraints experienced by the us government  httpirnavistarcomsecfilingcfmf