t as a result of the gas crises of the s bigblock gasoline v engines such as the ford  had begun to fall out of favor with pickuptruck buyers in the s diesel engines in american pickup trucks introduced by general motors in  had become popular as they offered the power of a bigblock v with the fuel economy of a smaller engine ford entered into a supply agreement with international harvester to receive its  l idi v engine the first dieselpowered ford pickup trucks debuted for  it was available for  and ton models gm at the time had a detroit diesel v engine also on its debut prior to that gm used a  diesel dodge started using a cummins sixcylinder in  in  when the international  l idi v was replaced by the te the diesel option was branded ford powerstroke to emphasize the switch to direct injection throughout the s and s ford offered internationalnavistar v as the dt inline was far too large to package in a pickup truck in the ford super duty pickup trucks as of  the  l ford powerstroke v was the last of the internationalnavistar diesels used in fords fseries super duty lineup when ford redesigned the super duty in  it was fitted with a  l v designed and produced by ford blue diamond truckedit in  navistar formed a joint venture with longtime  years customer ford motor company to manufacture mediumduty trucks and parts including diesel engines for both parent companies the new company blue diamond truck co llc operates in the navistar plant in general escobedo mexico its first products were the  ford f and f mediumduty trucks anhui jianghuai navistaredit on  september  anhui jianghuai automobile co ltd jac announced joint ventures with nc global and navistar international corporation that will develop build and market heavy duty trucks and diesel engines in china mahindra navistaredit main article mahindra navistar navistar formed a joint venture with mahindra  mahindra to build heavy trucks in india under the mahindra international brand which has since been renamed