 for fleet managers and ownersoperators its trucks are used in hauling drilling freight forwarding and pickup and delivery applications as well as fire department aviation residential construction and landscaping markets the company sells its products parts and services through a network of dealer outlets in the united states canada brazil mexico and internationally navistar inc was formerly known as international truck and engine corporation navistar inc was founded in  and is based in lisle illinois navistar inc operates as a subsidiary of navistar international corporation detailed description  navistar drivelisle il united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwinternationaltruckscom key executives for navistar inc mr troy a clarke chief executive officer and president age  mr walter g borst chief financial officer and executive vice president age  mr persio v lisboa president of operations age  mr g david gerrard ceo of chicago international trucks and president of chicago international trucks mr steve j keate president of the truck group compensation as of fiscal year  navistar inc key developments navistar international corporation and navistar inc enters into an amendment no  credit agreement apr   navistar international corporation parent and navistar incthe borrower entered into an amendment no  the term loan amendment to the credit agreement dated as of august   as amended and restated as of august   the term loan credit agreement among parent the borrower the lenders as defined therein party thereto and jpmorgan chase bank na jpmcb as administrative agent and collateral agent the borrower has determined that the adoption of the term loan amendment constituted a significant modification of the senior secured term loan for federal income tax purposes consequently for federal income tax purposes the borrower is deemed to have satisfied the senior secured term loan by issuing new indebtedness having the terms contained in the term loan amendment based on informati